modemMessageCannotBeParsed.description:
Message received from modem AAAA AAAA cannot be parsed!
This can be cause by multiple things:
- invalid configuration in the modem or the stored modem parameters in the system
- the message body could not be parsed by any of the assigned parsers

See the message below for more information:

Parsing failure: all assigned parsers have failed with the following errors:

 - Failed: 13 bytes were not parsed.
